{"tha-ap22:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap22:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap22:0.3":"Sumangalattheraapadana ","tha-ap22:1.1":"“Ahutim yitthukamoham, ","tha-ap22:1.2":"patiyadetvana bhojanam; ","tha-ap22:1.3":"Brahmane patimanento, ","tha-ap22:1.4":"visale malake thito. ","tha-ap22:2.1":"Athaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap22:2.2":"piyadassim mahayasam; ","tha-ap22:2.3":"Sabbalokavinetaram, ","tha-ap22:2.4":"sayambhum aggapuggalam. ","tha-ap22:3.1":"Bhagavantam jutimantam, ","tha-ap22:3.2":"savakehi purakkhatam; ","tha-ap22:3.3":"Adiccamiva rocantam, ","tha-ap22:3.4":"rathiyam patipannakam. ","tha-ap22:4.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap22:4.2":"sakam cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap22:4.3":"Manasava nimantesim, ","tha-ap22:4.4":"‘agacchatu mahamuni’. ","tha-ap22:5.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap22:5.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap22:5.3":"Khinasavasahassehi, ","tha-ap22:5.4":"mama dvaram upagami. ","tha-ap22:6.1":"Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap22:6.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","tha-ap22:6.3":"Pasadam abhiruhitva, ","tha-ap22:6.4":"sihasane nisidatam. ","tha-ap22:7.1":"Danto dantaparivaro, ","tha-ap22:7.2":"tinno tarayatam varo; ","tha-ap22:7.3":"Pasadam abhiruhitva, ","tha-ap22:7.4":"nisidi pavarasane. ","tha-ap22:8.1":"Yam me atthi sake gehe, ","tha-ap22:8.2":"amisam paccupatthitam; ","tha-ap22:8.3":"Taham buddhassa padasim, ","tha-ap22:8.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap22:9.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap22:9.2":"vedajato katanjali; ","tha-ap22:9.3":"Buddhasettham namassami, ","tha-ap22:9.4":"aho buddhassularata. ","tha-ap22:10.1":"Atthannam payirupasatam, ","tha-ap22:10.2":"bhunjam khinasava bahu; ","tha-ap22:10.3":"Tuyheveso anubhavo, ","tha-ap22:10.4":"saranam tam upemaham. ","tha-ap22:11.1":"Piyadassi ca bhagava, ","tha-ap22:11.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap22:11.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap22:11.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap22:12.1":"‘Yo so sangham abhojesi, ","tha-ap22:12.2":"ujubhutam samahitam; ","tha-ap22:12.3":"Tathagatanca sambuddham, ","tha-ap22:12.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap22:13.1":"Sattavisatikkhattum so, ","tha-ap22:13.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap22:13.3":"Sakakammabhiraddho so, ","tha-ap22:13.4":"devaloke ramissati. ","tha-ap22:14.1":"Dasa attha cakkhattum so, ","tha-ap22:14.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap22:14.3":"Pathabya rajjam pancasatam, ","tha-ap22:14.4":"vasudham avasissati’. ","tha-ap22:15.1":"Arannavanamoggayha, ","tha-ap22:15.2":"kananam byagghasevitam; ","tha-ap22:15.3":"Padhanam padahitvana, ","tha-ap22:15.4":"kilesa jhapita maya. ","tha-ap22:16.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap22:16.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap22:16.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap22:16.4":"bhattadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap22:17.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap22:17.2":"Vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap22:17.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap22:17.4":"Katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap22:18.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sumangalo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap22:19.1":"Sumangalattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap22:20.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap22:21.1":"Sihasani ekathambhi, ","tha-ap22:21.2":"nando ca culapanthako; ","tha-ap22:21.3":"Pilindarahulo ceva, ","tha-ap22:21.4":"vanganto ratthapalako. ","tha-ap22:22.1":"Sopako mangalo ceva, ","tha-ap22:22.2":"daseva dutiye vagge; ","tha-ap22:22.3":"Satanca atthatimsa ca, ","tha-ap22:22.4":"gatha cettha pakasita. ","tha-ap22:23.1":"Sihasaniyavaggo dutiyo. "}